title: Bloomberg Markets: Lelands to Auction Babe Ruth Memorabilia
itunes:title: Bloomberg Markets: Lelands to Auction Babe Ruth Memorabilia
description:
Bloomberg Markets with Carol Massar and Cory Johnson. GUEST: Joshua Evans Founder and Chairman Lelands.com Discussing Lelands 1st annual Invitational auction, featuring Babe Ruth's 1927 World Series ring and the 1919 contract that sold Ruth from the Red Sox to the Yankees.
